headline: Kyrgios Falls to Nadal After a Dazzling Display of Different Styles
abstract: Kyrgios seemed more motivated than ever at this Australian Open, but it was not enough to overcome a typically dogged performance from the top-seeded Nadal.
lead_paragraph: MELBOURNE, Australia â€” For two men who make their living traveling to the same places and pummeling balls across the same nets, Rafael Nadal and Nick Kyrgios have long appeared to have little in common.
